# ==============================================================================
# PNPM PACKAGE MANAGER CONFIG
# ==============================================================================
# Purpose: Enforces strict dependency resolution and version locking to
# ensure identical environments across all developer machines and CI/CD.
# ==============================================================================

# ==========================================
# 🔧 COMPATIBILITY (PNPM v10+)
# ==========================================
# Fixes ESLint VS Code extension not finding plugins with pnpm v10 node_modules structure
# See: https://github.com/microsoft/vscode-eslint/issues/1986#issuecomment-2799868163
public-hoist-pattern[]=*eslint-plugin*
